    "1101203": {
        "Desc": "Protect Teucer, find a way to meet up with him",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "I can't find him anywhere... where did he go..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I found your brother a moment ago."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Really? Where is he?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "He's already headed back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "What? Why... why would he leave without me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A huge number of people suddenly wanted to buy Mr. Cyclopses!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Y—Yeah, so he had to leave in a real hurry. He didn't abandon you here on purpose."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Oh... Th—That's great!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "But still, I was kinda hoping we could play here a little longer..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is for you. From your brother."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Mr. Cyclops will keep you company in his stead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Wow! Look at this!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "I never knew that they made Mr. Cyclopses in this size!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Look, it even has my name on it! It's my very own Mr. Cyclops!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You're really loving it, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "You bet! My brother is the best big brother ever!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You had a tour of Liyue, met your brother, visited the Institute of Toy Research, and got yourself a souvenir... Now that's what we tour guides call the perfect trip."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Do you think you're ready to head back to Snezhnaya now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Hehe... Don't worry, I know I can't get my way all the time. That'd just be annoying for everyone else."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "So... let's go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
