    "1101208": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Teucer",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Brother... someone was saying that Mr. Cyclops is a killing machine..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Were they, now? What a silly thing for them to say... And you shouldn't go repeating it either, Teucer, you're far too young to be talking about such violent topics."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Yeah, I knew that they were lying, anyways. Mr. Cyclops is here to defeat the bad guys and protect the world. He's my favorite toy!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Right. With Mr. Cyclops around, the bad guys won't ever get you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Hee-hee, that's right! Okay, I'm going to go play with Mr. Cyclops now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Hey, Teucer, wait up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Th—The door's shut! Will Teucer be alright?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "There's another path over there — let's move!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101206": {
        "Desc": "Return to Northland Bank",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "Teucer, see that big stone cube in front of you? I need your help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Yay! Do I really get to help my big brother out?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Childe",
                    "T": "You bet. Now, I'll count down from three, and then we touch it together. Ready? Three... two... one..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1101207": {
        "Desc": "Speak to the manager",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "This... This is everything I've ever dreamed of! It's Mr. Cyclops world!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "This is the surprise your brother prepared for you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Mr. Cyclops is the coolest!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow... He actually pulled it off! And the way he knocked those Ruin Guards around was like they really were kids' toys..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But Paimon wonders if he'll be alright after using Foul Legacy Transformation again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Awesome! Hee-hee!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Boy, if these Mr. Cyclopses weren't so big, I'd sure love to take one home."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Wait... Where'd he go? Where'd my brother go?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aren't you guys supposed to be playing hide-and-seek?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "Oh, that's right! I was so excited that I forgot all about our game!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Teucer",
                    "T": "#Well {M#mister}{F#lady}, let's look for him together, okay?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
